rows.label: qst202706_msg0002
rows.name:
Oh yeah, some of my Nopon friends
invited me to come along!

rows.label: qst202706_msg0003
rows.name:
They said everyone makes a circle,
and then they all lie down and sing!

rows.label: qst202706_msg0004
rows.name: They call that the Purpure Altar...

rows.label: qst202706_msg0005
rows.name:
It sounded awfully fun and cool and...!
But the leader said I couldn't come
in the end, 'cos I'm not a Nopon...
